## Instructions
Analyze this development data and identify recurring patterns or systemic issues. Provide a JSON response with a list of insights, where each insight has:
- insight_type: one of "recurring_bug", "slow_component", "tech_debt", "team_bottleneck", "regression_risk", "process_gap"
- title: concise title for the insight
- description: 2-3 sentence explanation
- evidence: list of objects with fields: type ("issue", "pr", "meeting"), id (number or string), detail (brief note)
- severity: "low", "medium", "high", or "critical"
- confidence: 0.0 to 1.0

Return a JSON object with a single field "insights" containing the list. Only include insights with confidence >= 0.5. Respond ONLY with valid JSON.